{"tid":179853,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好矛盾","createTime":"2017-03-30T13:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T14:21:57.000Z","uid":62284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af936a54fecc5e774ce1e0142a52134daab727b9","tid":179853,"uid":62284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇巴絲打都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日好易就對人有好感 但最後真係鍾意其實唔多<br />\n好易同人變到好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算之間曾經有幾曖昧<br />\n次次都係咁 有人追但自己又唔鍾意會抗拒<br />\n但自己鍾意親大家都冇開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家換咗新環境周街有人拍拖 自己就會有時都心郁郁<br />\n但最後都覺得自己一個好啲 享受自己咁嘅生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪冇得救 要孤獨終老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家係連點樣變close都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5f7d23871abf49f1a0a83474c749f25b1fc48f","tid":179853,"uid":62284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddda86f334a2a127d42d55bdccc8e621e153cf98","tid":179853,"uid":91728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"我都係好易對人有好感 亦都好易厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c84fd62d26e6b9f87b714bc71721e76e8071c4","tid":179853,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"這個世界最壞罪名 叫太易動情"}]}